<i>and nothin' to do.</i>

36:33.366 --> 36:35.465
<i> It's okay</i>
<i>to ask for help, Sally,</i>

36:35.500 --> 36:37.830
<i>we're just a phone call away.</i>

36:37.865 --> 36:41.966
