called someone," she says,
but doesn't wanna get involved.

39:23.998 --> 39:26.603
- Hm.
- I can't believe people
are like this.

39:26.638 --> 39:30.772
Well, write a poem about it.

39:30.807 --> 39:32.543
Isn't that what you do at Yale?

39:32.578 --> 39:35.139
No.
Sometimes we write essays.

39:35.174 --> 39:38.043
Well, get her statement.

39:38.078 --> 39:39.077
On it.

39:39.684 --> 39:40.947
Ma'am!

39:42.621 --> 39:43.917
One second.

39:49.122 --> 39:50.957
All right, Patterson.
We got what you need.

39:52.664 --> 39:55.093
<i>I'm worried about you, sis.</i>

39:55.128 --> 39:56.699
<i>You should</i>
<i>find a place to hide.</i>

39:56.734 --> 39:58.668
<i>One of the--</i>
<i>one of those big truck stops.</i>

39:58.703 --> 40:01.836
