when you get out.

40:22.661 --> 40:23.858
<i>I know, I know.</i>

40:23.893 --> 40:26.223
<i>That was the plan,</i>
<i>but it's not safe, sis.</i>

40:26.258 --> 40:28.258
<i>These guys</i>
<i>aren't fucking around.</i>

40:28.293 --> 40:31.767
Okay. Okay, so what do I do?

40:33.067 --> 40:35.199
Get across the border
and meet you?

40:35.234 --> 40:37.135
Where?

40:37.170 --> 40:39.577
<i>At home.</i>

40:39.612 --> 40:41.546
- Home?
<i>- Mm-hmm.</i>

40:41.581 --> 40:44.582
