40:44.617 --> 40:46.749
I haven't been there
since I was 15, I...

40:46.784 --> 40:48.784
I can't go back.

40:48.819 --> 40:50.852
<i>Dad's dead.</i>

40:50.887 --> 40:53.019
I know,
I paid for his fucking casket.

40:53.054 --> 40:57.188
- I'm not going.
