Neighbors say they saw the girls
walking around the neighborhood.

41:48.010 --> 41:49.108
I don't understand.

41:49.143 --> 41:52.815
Why didn't they...
call the police?

41:52.850 --> 41:56.016
Ask for help? Something.

41:56.051 --> 42:00.119
These kids have been
fucked over by the system
since the day they were born.

42:01.760 --> 42:03.221
They don't call the police.

42:04.730 --> 42:07.027
Nobody gives a shit
and they know it.

42:09.031 --> 42:13.198
