- A kid had been in this cage.
- What?

42:38.423 --> 42:42.227
A kid had been in this cage.
Bolted to the wall.

42:43.868 --> 42:46.066
Dog was running loose.

42:46.101 --> 42:47.364
From the looks of the dog,

42:47.399 --> 42:49.333
