to be aggressive.

42:49.368 --> 42:51.742
Traces of blood on the bolts.

42:53.405 --> 42:56.846
Looks like someone
tried to claw their way out.

42:56.881 --> 42:58.914
Fresh. Couple of days.

42:58.949 --> 43:00.883
We just missed them.

43:00.918 --> 43:02.346
Clothes in the cage.

43:02.381 --> 43:04.216
Pant size, dress size.

43:04.251 --> 43:07.285
She's probably about five feet.
Young.

43:07.320 --> 43:09.925
And she found a pencil
to doodle with.

43:46.733 --> 43:48.194
You know this place?

44:04.410 --> 44:06.311
This truck stop's so big...

44:08.084 --> 44:10.282
even the pimps
don't know their way around.

44:10.317 --> 44:12.416
We can hide here till tomorrow.

44:25.068 --> 44:26.232
Okay.

44:29.006 --> 44:30.808
Let's go over the ground rules.

44:35.782 --> 44:38.717
Hair spray,
AKA pepper spray.

44:40.182 --> 44:41.214
Here.

44:43.185 --> 44:46.219
Man's coat stays on
the driver's seat.

44:46.254 --> 44:47.759
Makes them think
a guy lives here.

44:48.927 --> 44:53.391
At night,
curtains closed, lights off.

44:53.426 --> 44:56.097
Lights on is an invitation.
Right?

44:56.132 --> 44:58.902
Someone knocks, we don't open.

44:58.937 --> 45:01.036
Doors locked. Windows up.

45:01.071 --> 45:04.776
Seatbelt wrapped through
the door handle

45:04.811 --> 45:07.878
and fastened
when we're sleepin'.

45:09.409 --> 45:12.883
You sleep up top.
I'm on the bottom. Got it?

45:12.918 --> 45:15.083
- Got it.
- I do the shoppin'.

45:15.118 --> 45:17.415
But you do the dishes.
You stay here.

45:17.450 --> 45:19.956
Don't let nobody see you, okay?

45:19.991 --> 45:21.760
- All right.
- That's it.

45:26.327 --> 45:27.931
But I need to go to the store.

45:27.966 --> 45:29.900
Uh, didn't you hear what I said?

45:29.935 --> 45:32.034
Your underwear is huge on me.

45:32.069 --> 45:34.773
Would you prefer me
to walk around
with 'em gathered in my ass?

45:41.309 --> 45:42.440
This it?

45:42.475 --> 45:44.948
It's for my niece.

45:44.983 --> 45:47.346
Well, how do you like that?

45:47.381 --> 45:50.855
I see you more than
I see my own family,

45:50.890 --> 45:53.451
