Ask for money!
We're all struggling here!

51:02.531 --> 51:03.430
I just wanna
take my kids to the--

51:03.466 --> 51:05.466
You got kids?
Go take care of them.

51:08.735 --> 51:12.176
- See?
- Yeah, I see.

51:12.211 --> 51:15.443
God... And what do you
want me to do?

51:15.478 --> 51:17.907
- Well--
- Resources
are so fucking scarce,

51:17.942 --> 51:20.580
