only infants and toddlers.

51:20.615 --> 51:22.681
Patterson, we can
catch these fucking guys.

51:22.716 --> 51:24.914
It's you and Sterling, Gerick.
That is it.

51:24.949 --> 51:29.226
If we don't bring 'em down now,
they just set up some place else
and then what?

51:29.261 --> 51:31.228
Ten more girls?
Fifteen?

51:32.693 --> 51:34.396
Trafficking will not go away

51:34.431 --> 51:35.661
until people stop buying,
Gerick.

51:35.696 --> 51:37.663
We know that.
All right?

51:37.698 --> 51:39.533
We get these guys
and someone else

51:39.568 --> 51:41.502
is just gonna satisfy
the demand.

51:48.940 --> 51:51.182
It could be your daughter,
Patterson.

52:01.359 --> 52:04.393
Hi. I saw you earlier today.

52:04.428 --> 52:10.399
