52:15.703 --> 52:19.177
M-maybe later? We're in
the pink RV over by the store.

52:21.709 --> 52:25.183
Okay, well, maybe later.

52:25.977 --> 52:27.746
Bye then. See ya.

53:28.578 --> 53:29.973
Wow.

53:31.845 --> 53:34.384
Who knew she
could still shine.

53:49.027 --> 53:50.565
You said he would help.

53:50.600 --> 53:53.370
You don't read
other people's letters.

53:53.405 --> 53:55.339
He's in fucking jail,
so how's he gonna help us?

53:57.871 --> 54:00.806
What do you mean? "Us"?

54:02.348 --> 54:03.908
You and me are not "us".

54:05.483 --> 54:07.912
The only "us" I know
is me and my brother.

54:12.754 --> 54:15.623
Why didn't you tell me
he was in jail?

54:15.658 --> 54:17.856
He's getting
out of jail tomorrow.

54:17.891 --> 54:20.397
'Cause of you,
I can't be there.

54:23.369 --> 54:25.402
You could've just told me.

54:25.437 --> 54:27.338
None of your fucking business.

54:49.461 --> 54:52.561
Like looking for a needle
in a haystack.

54:52.596 --> 54:54.695
A semi is no needle though.

54:54.730 --> 54:56.928
