55:28.698 --> 55:31.028
You're driving. Let's go.

56:57.281 --> 56:58.918
- Hello.
- <i> Oh, shit.</i>

56:58.953 --> 57:01.591
<i>I was worried about you.</i>
<i>I worked it out.</i>

57:01.626 --> 57:02.955
<i>We gotta get the girl</i>
<i>back to them,</i>

57:02.990 --> 57:04.528
<i>and they'll let us</i>
<i>off the hook.</i>

57:04.563 --> 57:06.596
<i>- Where you at?</i>
- Sherrigan's.

57:06.631 --> 57:08.730
Heading to Arkansas tomorrow
like you told me.

57:08.765 --> 57:11.260
<i>Okay. Okay.</i>
<i>Everything good there?</i>

57:11.295 --> 57:16.804
- Yeah. All's good.
<i>- Great. Okay.</i>

57:16.839 --> 57:19.906
- I love you.
-<i> I love you, too.</i>

57:19.941 --> 57:23.173
<i>Just keep the girl close.</i>
<i>She's our lifeline, sis.</i>

57:23.208 --> 57:25.142
- Yeah.
-<i> Okay, I'll see you tomorrow.</i>

57:25.177 --> 57:27.815
- Yeah.
