1:03:00.116 --> 1:03:02.314
That maybe
you'll always be lonely

1:03:02.349 --> 1:03:05.856
because no one knows the world
the same as you do?

1:03:08.322 --> 1:03:09.860
Uh...

1:03:18.431 --> 1:03:20.101
