We lock 'em up, and we're just
creating a breeding ground.

1:30:39.873 --> 1:30:43.105
It's a long straight ball
to center field!

1:30:43.140 --> 1:30:46.075
Home run!

1:30:51.786 --> 1:30:53.280
Oh, come here.

1:30:59.090 --> 1:31:02.025
Hey. What'd they do to you?

1:31:02.060 --> 1:31:05.633
Hey. Can't you smile anymore?

1:31:13.742 --> 1:31:16.105
Oh. Oh, wow.

1:31:16.140 --> 1:31:19.174
She is-- she is really young.

1:31:21.112 --> 1:31:22.782
When do we go meet 'em?

1:31:25.083 --> 1:31:29.217
Well, they told me
bring her out to the airfield
about eleven o'clock.

1:31:38.932 --> 1:31:40.635
Here, here.

1:31:40.670 --> 1:31:42.538
Why don't you
have a seat right there?

1:31:56.653 --> 1:31:57.982
Remember that?

1:32:06.355 --> 1:32:08.157
I'm sorry
I can't get you anything.

1:32:08.192 --> 1:32:10.599
You know, nobody's been here
for the past couple of years

1:32:10.634 --> 1:32:12.293
since... since our dad died.

1:32:12.328 --> 1:32:14.064
That's fine.

1:32:33.789 --> 1:32:35.624
That. Don't you touch that.

1:32:35.659 --> 1:32:37.725
- Get your paws off my trophy.

1:32:57.010 --> 1:32:59.010
You know, I was-- I was--

1:32:59.045 --> 1:33:00.946
I was happy when you got away.

1:33:02.180 --> 1:33:03.278
- I was.
- I know.

1:33:06.987 --> 1:33:10.252
I didn't have to--
I didn't have to think about...

1:33:10.287 --> 1:33:13.321
listening to something happen
to you every night.

1:33:29.779 --> 1:33:31.845
It's not as bad as I thought.

1:33:33.717 --> 1:33:36.751
I mean, the mess is as bad
as I thought it'd be, but...

1:33:44.123 --> 1:33:45.386
It doesn't scare me anymore.

1:33:46.323 --> 1:33:47.960
Well, that's good to hear.

1:33:52.131 --> 1:33:55.330
Should we, uh...
should we get going?

1:33:55.365 --> 1:33:57.431
Sure. Where?

1:34:04.913 --> 1:34:06.308
You're right about me,
you know.

1:34:08.983 --> 1:34:10.081
What?

1:34:11.348 --> 1:34:13.216
I know nothing about this.

1:34:15.990 --> 1:34:17.891
Grew up with a silver spoon.

1:34:18.993 --> 1:34:21.488
Completely disconnected.

1:34:21.523 --> 1:34:23.457
And the strongest memory
I have of my mom

1:34:23.492 --> 1:34:27.395
was her picture
hanging above my crib.

1:34:27.430 --> 1:34:31.036
And I joined the bureau so I
could mean something to someone.

1:34:32.941 --> 1:34:34.941
Can't say that's working out.

1:34:38.276 --> 1:34:39.715
Why'd you join?

1:34:41.851 --> 1:34:43.510
Doesn't matter why I joined.

1:34:43.545 --> 1:34:46.018
Only matters what I do with it.

1:34:52.928 --> 1:34:53.960
Yeah.

1:34:55.095 --> 1:34:56.490
What?

1:34:56.525 --> 1:34:59.735
Yeah, okay. Yeah.

1:35:01.398 --> 1:35:04.465
Hospital has Sally on file.
Over 30 years ago.

1:35:04.500 --> 1:35:08.876
Numerous ER visits,
various, um... accidents.

1:35:08.911 --> 1:35:10.779
She was brought in
by her brother.

1:35:10.814 --> 1:35:12.242
There's a home address.

1:35:16.952 --> 1:35:22.219
Uh... I don't wanna
give her back.

1:35:22.254 --> 1:35:24.056
I wanna buy her out.

1:35:26.225 --> 1:35:27.389
The girl?

1:35:27.424 --> 1:35:28.995
Leila, yeah.

1:35:31.934 --> 1:35:34.330
Well, what are you
gonna do with her?

1:35:35.597 --> 1:35:37.036
Where are you
gonna get the money?

1:35:37.071 --> 1:35:38.565
I have some money.

1:35:38.600 --> 1:35:39.940
How much?

1:35:42.010 --> 1:35:43.504
How'd you get it?

1:35:43.539 --> 1:35:47.112
Enough. I should have some
left over, too.

1:35:47.147 --> 1:35:49.312
- Mm-hmm.
- How did you get it?

1:35:52.317 --> 1:35:54.185
How'd you get the money, Sal?

1:35:55.122 --> 1:35:56.792
Sold my trailer.

1:36:11.941 --> 1:36:13.336
She needs us.

1:36:14.911 --> 1:36:16.812
The way we needed each other.

1:36:19.278 --> 1:36:22.246
You mean like a--
like a family or something?

1:36:28.485 --> 1:36:29.990
Well...

1:36:30.025 --> 1:36:31.354
Well, that would take me

1:36:31.389 --> 1:36:34.192
just a little bit of time
to get used to.

1:36:34.227 --> 1:36:35.391
You know?

1:36:38.033 --> 1:36:39.131
Yeah.

1:36:50.342 --> 1:36:52.210
All right.

1:36:52.245 --> 1:36:55.279
We do this, you gotta let me
take care of it, all right?

1:36:55.314 --> 1:36:56.643
I'm gonna bring 'em the cash.

1:36:56.678 --> 1:36:59.217
Pay. Done.

1:37:00.616 --> 1:37:03.386
All right. Okay.

1:37:07.458 --> 1:37:09.062
Where's the bathroom?

1:37:09.097 --> 1:37:11.460
We're-we're gonna
take a little ride. Uh...

1:37:11.495 --> 1:37:15.464
No. No.
Leila stays with me.

1:37:15.499 --> 1:37:18.401
No, that's not
how it works, sis.
I gotta bring her.

1:37:18.436 --> 1:37:21.173
You-you could've taken her
to the police
for all they know.

1:37:21.208 --> 1:37:23.373
All right. I'll go then.

1:37:23.408 --> 1:37:25.342
No, Sal. Sal.

1:37:25.377 --> 1:37:27.575
If she's going, I'm going.
Uh, Leila, let's go.

1:37:27.610 --> 1:37:29.544
- Sal.
- I still have to pee.

1:37:29.579 --> 1:37:31.282
It's-it's just right here.

1:37:31.317 --> 1:37:34.120
- Useless...
- I'll turn the truck around.

1:37:34.155 --> 1:37:35.253
It's just a bad idea.

1:37:35.288 --> 1:37:36.419
Get out of your pajamas.

1:37:36.454 --> 1:37:37.585
It's time to go.

1:37:48.499 --> 1:37:51.137
<i>Joining conference now.</i>

1:37:51.172 --> 1:37:52.369
Sally's here.

1:37:52.404 --> 1:37:54.305
Hi, Sally.

1:37:54.340 --> 1:37:56.109
<i>Dolly's here with us.</i>

1:37:56.144 --> 1:37:58.573
That's right, Rose.
Pattie's here, too.

1:37:58.608 --> 1:38:01.609
<i>She's slow as a little turtle,</i>
<i>just like you, Sally.</i>

1:38:01.644 --> 1:38:04.480
Come on, baby doll, get with it.

1:38:04.515 --> 1:38:06.680
- <i> I'm just sayin'.</i>
- <i> Shut up, Dolly.</i>

1:38:06.715 --> 1:38:10.156
<i>Sally's got some serious</i>
<i>business to take care of.</i>

1:38:10.191 --> 1:38:11.553
<i>Where are you headed?</i>

1:38:11.588 --> 1:38:15.161
Remember that old airport?
Southeast?

1:38:15.196 --> 1:38:17.361
Hell yeah,
I remember that place.

1:38:17.396 --> 1:38:21.134
Yeah, me too, I was gonna be
a flight attendant
before I broke my teeth.

1:38:24.238 --> 1:38:30.077
Just wanna tell ya,
it's good to know you ladies
are out there.

1:38:30.112 --> 1:38:32.244
We're always out here.

1:38:32.279 --> 1:38:33.674
<i>Come rain or come shine.</i>

1:38:42.355 --> 1:38:45.389
Dennis? Leila?

1:38:47.261 --> 1:38:48.491
Let's go!

1:38:50.297 --> 1:38:51.461
You look fucked up.

1:38:51.496 --> 1:38:53.463
Huh? Oh, yeah?

1:38:53.498 --> 1:38:56.367
Oh, yeah.
Freezing out there.

1:38:56.402 --> 1:38:59.238
Well, Leila found something.
I think you're gonna like it.

1:39:03.310 --> 1:39:06.014
Sal, what are you doin'?

1:39:09.316 --> 1:39:10.744
What are you doin'?

1:39:10.779 --> 1:39:13.153
It's-it's-it's-it's the dress

1:39:13.188 --> 1:39:15.518
that dad bought you
for your 13th birthday.

1:39:15.553 --> 1:39:17.355
I thought you'd like it.

1:39:17.390 --> 1:39:20.259
- I thought you'd like it, Sal.
- Take it off.
Take it off, Leila.

1:39:20.294 --> 1:39:21.656
Sal-- I-I thought
you'd think it was cute.

1:39:21.691 --> 1:39:22.657
I thought you'd like it.
I--

1:39:22.692 --> 1:39:24.527
- I don't!
- All right, all right,

1:39:24.562 --> 1:39:27.629
- I fucked up. I'm sorry!
- Take it off!

1:40:16.482 --> 1:40:17.547
It's clear.

1:40:37.899 --> 1:40:39.107
Hair.

1:40:40.836 --> 1:40:42.308
They were here.

1:40:44.510 --> 1:40:45.509
We missed 'em.

1:40:48.316 --> 1:40:52.186
Shit, shit, shit, shit.
Shit!

1:41:17.774 --> 1:41:18.839
I'll go.

1:41:34.263 --> 1:41:35.493
Where's the girl?

1:41:35.528 --> 1:41:37.165
I wanna buy her out.

1:41:38.894 --> 1:41:40.432
That wasn't the deal.

1:41:40.467 --> 1:41:42.368
I'll pay more
than the going rate.

1:41:43.734 --> 1:41:44.700
Let me see her.

1:41:44.735 --> 1:41:45.767
No.

1:41:49.377 --> 1:41:51.410
- Come on.
- Dennis!

1:41:53.843 --> 1:41:55.414
I have the cash.

1:41:57.748 --> 1:41:59.517
But I need to know
we're cut clean.

1:42:00.586 --> 1:42:03.257
My brother, me, the girl.

1:42:03.292 --> 1:42:04.885
And we don't see you anymore.

1:42:08.429 --> 1:42:11.925
Sure. You bought it, you own it.

1:42:23.004 --> 1:42:26.478
Really? You think I'm just
gonna let you take the girl?

1:42:26.513 --> 1:42:28.645
How do I know you won't talk?

1:42:28.680 --> 1:42:31.318
'Cause I'm just as guilty
as everybody else.

1:42:33.685 --> 1:42:35.619
- That's it, just get the girl
and let's get out of here!

1:42:35.654 --> 1:42:37.984
Don't hurt my sister!
I said, don't hurt my sister!

1:42:38.019 --> 1:42:39.722
- Back here!
- Hey.

1:42:39.757 --> 1:42:40.954
Get the girl
and let's go!

1:42:40.989 --> 1:42:42.494
- Hey!

1:42:44.025 --> 1:42:44.924
- Hey!
- Fuck!

1:42:44.960 --> 1:42:47.334
- Hey! Easy.

1:42:47.369 --> 1:42:49.369
- Den--
- Hey! Get off her!

1:42:49.404 --> 1:42:50.568
- Get off her! Hey!
- Fuck you!

1:42:50.603 --> 1:42:52.306
- Hey, go easy!
- Get him!

1:42:55.443 --> 1:42:57.509
Dennis, what?

1:43:00.415 --> 1:43:03.911
I said-- I told him
not to hurt my sister.

1:43:03.946 --> 1:43:06.012
You said to make it look real!

1:43:06.047 --> 1:43:09.323
Not that real!
I said don't hurt my sister!

1:43:09.358 --> 1:43:12.623
You didn't have to kill him!

1:43:12.658 --> 1:43:15.395
Why couldn't you just get
the fucking kid, Claire? Huh?

1:43:17.465 --> 1:43:19.432
I told you exactly where
she was!

1:43:19.467 --> 1:43:21.401
- Now get in the van!
- Let go!

1:43:21.436 --> 1:43:22.534
- Dennis?
- Let go of me!

1:43:22.569 --> 1:43:23.568
You-you weren't
supposed to see this.

1:43:23.604 --> 1:43:25.999
- No, Sal. Sal, listen, Sal--
- Let go of me!

1:43:26.034 --> 1:43:27.572
- Dennis--
- Let go of me!

1:43:27.607 --> 1:43:30.443
Stop it! Sal, you weren't
supposed to see this.

1:43:30.478 --> 1:43:32.379
Sal. Sal, no! Let her go!

1:43:32.414 --> 1:43:33.842
Let her go! Let her go.

1:43:35.012 --> 1:43:37.912
I was just gonna do it for a bit
till we got on our feet.

1:43:37.947 --> 1:43:40.486
Sal, you were not
supposed to see this.

1:43:40.521 --> 1:43:43.588
Get in the fucking van, Claire!

1:43:46.923 --> 1:43:48.461
Sal...

1:43:48.496 --> 1:43:49.594
Please...

1:43:49.629 --> 1:43:51.629
Claire, get in the van.

1:43:54.634 --> 1:43:56.436
- Please.
- Let me get rid of her, okay?

1:43:56.471 --> 1:43:57.866
Just let me get rid of her,

1:43:57.901 --> 1:44:01.309
and-and we get back to us,
Sal, I promise.

1:44:01.344 --> 1:44:03.311
You'll see, it's gonna be fine.

1:44:03.346 --> 1:44:04.972
No, Sally!

1:44:05.007 --> 1:44:06.545
Sal, it's gonna be okay.

1:44:06.580 --> 1:44:08.547
Sally! Please!

1:44:11.453 --> 1:44:13.915
No!

1:44:16.821 --> 1:44:20.493
Dennis, stop! Stop! Don't!

1:44:23.828 --> 1:44:25.025
Leila!

1:44:31.572 --> 1:44:32.835
Leila!

1:45:00.161 --> 1:45:02.370
Leila. Leila.

1:45:07.003 --> 1:45:08.937
Sally?

1:45:08.972 --> 1:45:10.510
Come on, Sal!

1:45:13.141 --> 1:45:14.514
Come on, Sal!

1:45:14.549 --> 1:45:16.076
Fly away with me.

1:45:18.047 --> 1:45:20.454
Come fly away with me.

1:45:20.489 --> 1:45:21.983
We'll go to Mars...

1:45:22.018 --> 1:45:26.119
Saturn, and we'll go
to Jupiter and China.

1:45:26.154 --> 1:45:28.891
Anywhere but here.
We get the hell outta here.

1:45:33.469 --> 1:45:35.898
We're just a couple of kids.

1:45:35.933 --> 1:45:38.131
- Kids... Sal?

1:45:38.166 --> 1:45:39.440
No, Dennis.

1:45:40.135 --> 1:45:41.508
They are kids.

1:45:42.709 --> 1:45:44.544
Not us.

1:45:45.910 --> 1:45:47.910
How much you sell 'em for?

1:45:47.945 --> 1:45:50.451
- No.
- How much a job?

1:45:50.486 --> 1:45:52.145
- No.
- How many times a day?

1:45:52.180 --> 1:45:54.114
No, you-you
got it all wrong.

1:45:54.149 --> 1:45:55.918
Sal, I do it for you.
I do it for you!

1:45:55.953 --> 1:45:58.085
- No!
- I-- Everything I do...

1:46:04.566 --> 1:46:05.994
I want you to tell me...

1:46:07.569 --> 1:46:10.636
what-what that girl
does for you that I don't do.

1:46:13.069 --> 1:46:14.772
What do you owe her?

1:46:14.807 --> 1:46:16.675
She doesn't owe me anything.

1:46:39.667 --> 1:46:40.765
Sal...

1:46:42.571 --> 1:46:43.900
Hey, Sal.

1:47:14.933 --> 1:47:16.537
Let's get you in the car.

1:47:16.572 --> 1:47:17.736
Watch your head, all right?

1:47:22.039 --> 1:47:23.038
Hey.

1:47:30.916 --> 1:47:32.146
Worried about him?

1:47:36.218 --> 1:47:37.855
Never gonna stop.

1:47:40.321 --> 1:47:42.563
Well, if we can
get him to help us...

1:47:44.061 --> 1:47:46.061
maybe we can catch the big guy.

1:47:48.934 --> 1:47:51.737
Promise you'll take care
of those kids.

1:47:51.772 --> 1:47:55.741
Oh, don't worry.
I'll see to them.

1:47:55.776 --> 1:47:57.710
That's what gets me
up in the morning.

1:48:03.850 --> 1:48:08.952
Well, you...
probably better get going.

1:48:08.987 --> 1:48:10.789
Local police are on their way.

1:48:12.793 --> 1:48:14.694
We have your statement, so...

1:48:20.702 --> 1:48:22.064
Have a nice ride.

1:48:40.282 --> 1:48:42.150
You know, we're gonna
get in trouble for this.

1:48:43.252 --> 1:48:45.186
I'm gonna get
in trouble for this.

1:48:45.221 --> 1:48:46.726
You didn't know
shit about it.

1:48:48.059 --> 1:48:50.565
It's not your fault
if I went rogue.

1:48:54.362 --> 1:48:56.098
You're still an asshole.

1:49:00.104 --> 1:49:01.202
To you.

1:49:17.121 --> 1:49:18.252
Seatbelt?
